criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  aged 18 years old or above

          -  diagnosed with stomach or colon cancer;

          -  at the initial of receiving chemotherapy treatment;

          -  indicated for oral feeding;

          -  not having co-morbidities of chronic diseases such as kidney failure, heart failure,
             liver failure, diabetes;

          -  having ability to communicate with data collectors and both attending doctors and
             agreeing to involve in the study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  treated by other methods such as radiation, endocrine, immunity;

          -  undergoing terminal palliative care;

          -  having contraindications to oral feeding/enteral nutrition
